    "description": "<strong>Hoglands</strong> 是一款具有角色扮演元素动态策略游戏，在阴暗的中世纪环境中设置了精美的手绘图形。您将被投入到一头高贵的野猪的冒险中，试图保护您的王国免受成群的不死生物的侵害，并找出瘟疫蔓延的原因。由您来建立防御以抵御夜间攻击并在白天收集资源。不要忘记尝试摧毁将您的臣民变成嗜血怪物的瘟疫之源。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态战斗</h2>每一秒都很重要，因为您的敌人随着每一波新浪潮变得越来越强大。如果您不想让吸血鬼在晚上攻击您，就在白天猎杀吸血鬼。游戏在白天和黑夜之间交替，相应地向一个或另一个方向改变游戏的平衡。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210240/extras/8058c6824c9ba8c89c3f6de2bcf88fe0.poster.avif?t=1764184342\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210240/extras/8058c6824c9ba8c89c3f6de2bcf88fe0.webm?t=1764184342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立您的军队</h2>收集资源并快速构建防御工事，因为夜幕降临，您的敌人肯定会在您最意想不到的时候发动攻击。招募并武装您的幸存者同伴。您将需要他们来防御和突袭敌人的巢穴。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210240/extras/04474f2217fc72e4fd6fcee6fe9257bf.poster.avif?t=1764184342\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210240/extras/04474f2217fc72e4fd6fcee6fe9257bf.webm?t=1764184342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >向邪恶之神献祭</h2>在一场殊死的战斗中，您需要盟友，牺牲你的臣民以获得奖励，让你离胜利更近一步。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210240/extras/d0ecb8f812bd55d29f3fcf564a7077bd.poster.avif?t=1764184342\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2210240/extras/d0ecb8f812bd55d29f3fcf564a7077bd.webm?t=1764184342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>你有勇气和技巧去面对吸血伯爵德古拉本人吗?",
